ref=\"https://crypto.cnyes.com/BTC/24h\" target=\"_blank\">Bitcoin</a> (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ABTC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ABTC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ABTC-US</a>)</li>\n</ul></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>能源 / 核能政策</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul>\n<li>Constellation Energy (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CEG:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CEG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CEG-US</a>)</li>\n</ul></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"warning\">(本文不開放合作夥伴轉載)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
